---
// R1 hub — links to the motion prototypes. Deliberately plain: the
// prototypes are the show, this is just the door.
---

<html lang="en">
  <head>
    <meta charset="utf-8" />
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1, viewport-fit=cover" />
    <meta name="robots" content="noindex" />
    <meta name="theme-color" content="#FFEDDB" />
    <title>R1 prototypes · Tres.</title>
    <link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.googleapis.com" />
    <link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.gstatic.com" crossorigin />
    <link
      href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Archivo:wght@500;600&family=Newsreader:ital,opsz,wght@0,16..72,400;1,16..72,400&family=Space+Mono&display=swap"
      rel="stylesheet"
    />
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="/v2-tokens.css" />
  </head>
  <body>
    <main>
      <p class="spec">tres.studio — rebrand · R1</p>
      <h1 class="title">Motion prototypes</h1>
      <p class="lede">
        Three ideas to feel, on a phone if possible. None of this touches the
        site itself.
      </p>

      <nav class="list">
        <a class="item" href="/r1/blob">
          <span class="item-name">Blob scroll</span>
          <span class="item-note">The five Work projects behind a breathing mask. Judge the pace.</span>
        </a>
        <a class="item" href="/r1/button">
          <span class="item-name">Back button</span>
          <span class="item-note">Tracks your cursor on desktop, sits still under a thumb.</span>
        </a>
        <a class="item" href="/r1/ticker">
          <span class="item-name">Ticker</span>
          <span class="item-note">The visit counter as flat flip cards, on the real count.</span>
        </a>
      </nav>
    </main>

    <style is:inline>
      * { margin: 0; box-sizing: border-box; }
      html { background: var(--v2-cream, #FFEDDB); }
      body {
        font-family: var(--v2-body, Georgia, serif);
        color: var(--v2-ink, #2B1F1A);
        -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased;
      }
      ::selection { background: var(--v2-sand, #EDCDBB); }

      main { max-width: 620px; margin: 0 auto; padding: 18svh var(--v2-pad, 24px) 20svh; }
      .spec { font-family: var(--v2-mono, monospace); font-size: 12px; color: var(--v2-ink-soft, #6b5c54); }
      .title {
        font-family: var(--v2-display, sans-serif); font-weight: 600;
        font-size: clamp(34px, 6.4vw, 56px); line-height: 1;
        text-transform: uppercase; text-wrap: balance; margin-top: 10px;
      }
      .lede { font-size: 18px; font-style: italic; color: var(--v2-ink-soft, #6b5c54); margin-top: 14px; text-wrap: pretty; }

      .list { display: block; margin-top: 8svh; border-top: 1px solid var(--v2-hairline, rgba(43,31,26,0.16)); }
      .item {
        display: block;
        padding: 26px 0;
        border-bottom: 1px solid var(--v2-hairline, rgba(43,31,26,0.16));
        color: inherit; text-decoration: none;
      }
      .item-name {
        display: block;
        font-family: var(--v2-display, sans-serif); font-weight: 600;
        font-size: clamp(22px, 3.6vw, 30px); text-transform: uppercase;
        transition: translate var(--v2-ui, 200ms) var(--v2-out, ease-out);
      }
      .item-note { display: block; font-size: 16px; font-style: italic; color: var(--v2-ink-soft, #6b5c54); margin-top: 6px; text-wrap: pretty; }
      @media (hover: hover) and (pointer: fine) {
        .item:hover .item-name { translate: 6px 0; }
      }
      .item:active .item-name { translate: 3px 0; }
    </style>
  </body>
</html>
